<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l8">hag <expan>Pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Scherdıng </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_287_r1l9"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>VVernh<ex>er</ex></expan> Neẅmeyrs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l10">dem wir nehſt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒulıeb geleyt ʒu vns geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l11">maynt . wıe <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>wernh<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein brıef ʒu vns gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> mayne ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l12"><expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm recht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l13">vns <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Neẅmeyr auch <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>deſſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> brıefs wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l14">ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ doch eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> dabey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l15">prüfen vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mag . wıe der man geſıtt ıſt vnd daʒ er Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l16">fremd ſache fürnymbt / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır niht ſache <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l17">er in <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>heıt</expan> ʒu vns ſprüch habe / Deẅht Jn aber daʒ er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l18">ʒu vns ıcht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett / <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er vns vngerechfertıgt niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l19"><expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt . ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır Jm <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> rechten ſein / vor dem <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l20"><expan>durchleẅchtıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sıgmund<ex>en</ex></expan> Römiſchem ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l21"><expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd ʒu Beheim etc kunıg <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l22">der dreyer Reıchs Stette <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> winſheim <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l23">Rate einem als wir denn gefreyet ſeyn vnd als wır das vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l24">auch <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / hat er denn ʒu <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıcht ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l25"><expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd wıl <expan>ſein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l26">briefen . <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu vns ſenden . dem <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l27"><expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> / vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_288" id="143r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l2"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen . wenn wır des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l3">den er ʒu <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett anheim ſeyn on geuerd . Denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l4"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l5"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_287" id="142v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Hag, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
